<H3 ALIGN="CENTER"><CENTER>ORGANIZATIONS</CENTER></H3>

<p>
<i>
Citizens for Health.  
</I>
Tacoma, WA. 800-357-2211.
<p>

<HR>
<H3 ALIGN="CENTER"><CENTER>PROGRAMS</CENTER></H3>


<p>
Matthias Rath, 
<I>
Health Now, 
</I>
387 Ivy Street, San Francisco CA 94102. 1-800-624-2442.
<P>
See 
<I>
Alternative Medicine Yellow Pages 
</I>
for additional practitioners and resources for your hearthealth.


  <!-- --[ End article ]-- -->



</blockquote>

