       For more on Dr. Golchehreh, see "Preventing Midlife Diabetes and Heart Disease," Digest No. 13, pp. 62-63, 66-67. To contact him: Ira J. Golchehreh, Lic.Ac., O.M.D., Bay Park Business Center, 2175 Francisco Blvd., Suite D, San Rafael, CA 94901; tel: 415-485-4411; fax: 415-485-0857.      
   </td>
  </tr>

